# Rock Paper Scissors Game

A simple console-based Rock Paper Scissors game built with Python.  
Features:

- Play against the computer
- Short input options (r/p/s)
- Score tracking
- Best-of-3 mode
- Loading animation and ASCII title for fun

## How to Play

1. Run the Python script.
2. Enter your choice: rock, paper, scissors (or r/p/s).
3. Try to beat the computer! The first to 2 wins the game.
4. Enjoy and have fun! ðŸŽ®

